    <item>
      <title>前高盛银行家 Heyman 被任命为 Desmarais 可持续能源公司首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ex-goldman-banker-heyman-becomes-ceo-of-desmarais-firm-power-sustainable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Power Sustainable 是一家由加拿大亿万富翁 Desmarais 家族控制的投资公司，该公司任命 Bruce Heyman 为首席执行官，负责吸引更多来自全球机构投资者的资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ex-goldman-banker-heyman-becomes-ceo-of-desmarais-firm-power-sustainable</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 14:37:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利央行在福林贬值后承诺实施“有限”绿色计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hungarian-central-bank-pledges-limited-green-program-after-forint-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利央行承诺维持“严谨而紧缩”的货币政策，以缓解投资者的担忧，因为福林跌至一年半以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hungarian-central-bank-pledges-limited-green-program-after-forint-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:08:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
